Ranger Help for: desertsurvival
================================

SYNTAX:      desertsurvival
             desert survival
USAGE:       Souvrael desert and other extreme desert terrain
SLOT COST:   14
BASE SP:     10
SKILL TYPE:  cartography

SUMMARY:
This skill toggles desert survival instincts on or off. When active,
the Ranger reads the heat, wind, shade, and pace of the desert well
enough to avoid the punishing Souvrael desert heat that normally drains
water or damages travelers caught without water.

Use this before crossing the Segovia Desert, the Rub' al Khali, or other
Souvrael desert rooms that punish unprepared travelers. Toggle it again
to relax those instincts.

